com.samsung.android.sdk.health.sensor

Interface ShealthSensorDevice.EventListener

  • Enclosing class:
    ShealthSensorDevice

    public static interface ShealthSensorDevice.EventListener
    This listener interface receives joining and leaving status events and command response events.
